What's my lunch today? Nasi Lemak from @changinasilemak
.
Changi Nasi Lemak are available for delivery islandwide at a flat rate of $5.00
.
▪️Spicy Thigh Cutlet Set (McSpicy-Inspired)
▪️Chicken Wing Set
▪️Curry Chicken Set (Drumstick)
.
Visit https://changinasilemak.oddle.me/en_SG/ for more info.
.
